1102.name: AlSi 5 Tig
1102.Applications: Tig filler metal for welding Aluminium alloys with maximum 2% alloying elements and for aluminium alloys containing up to 7% Si.(after anodizing welding will be of a dark grey colour)
1102.Suitable_For: AlMgSi 0, AlSiMg (A), AlSi 1 MgMn, AlMg1SiCu, 3.3206, 3.3210, 3.2315, 3.3211, EN AW 6060, EN AW 6005A, EN AW 6082, EN AW 6061, EN AC 45000,
